{"tid":664653,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"飄雨中歌唱的仙女 長髮IU精彩舞台","createTime":"2018-05-14T09:03:40.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-18T13:47:02.000Z","uid":34643,"like":23,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"5ff7b9c8301f300d110808ef94a3a5fdca32018f","tid":664653,"uid":34643,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-14T09:03:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://ww4.sinaimg.cn/bmiddle/82ca9a40gy1fr8876cx9rj20u01hcqnw.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fww4.sinaimg.cn%2Fbmiddle%2F82ca9a40gy1fr8876cx9rj20u01hcqnw.jpg&h=67e4249c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n12日晚，IU出席了在韓國京畿道加平Jara島舉行的&ldquo;真露LIVE FESTIVAL&rdquo;活動，壓軸登場的IU為現場觀眾帶來了七首個人熱曲的精彩舞台。特別的是原本只准備了四首歌曲的公演最後唱了七首，還特別清唱了兩首歌。就算是在大暴雨中歌唱也為了粉絲把舞台做到最好，真是大暖女一枚！<br />\n<br />\n歌單:<br />\n1.周五見<br />\n2.你和我<br />\n3.夜信<br />\n4.好日子<br />\n5.你的意義<br />\n6.Palette<br />\n7.Rain Drop(無伴奏)<br />\n8.這一刻(無伴奏)<br />\n9.無法入眠的雨夜<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/bOQHNiK.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FbOQHNiK.jpg&h=a258d00c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/v55I1Pb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2Fv55I1Pb.jpg&h=d4de208f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/IQI22MO.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FIQI22MO.jpg&h=cf5e1065&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/6cDLaZs.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2F6cDLaZs.jpg&h=6e9b6368&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/oNMSPAS.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FoNMSPAS.jpg&h=e3e1215e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/Q8LMUqh.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FQ8LMUqh.jpg&h=ee27742c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/7tkUpn5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\